{"tid":2074617,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新書出版前首次受訪 波頓：盼川普只做一任","createTime":"2020-06-22T08:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T12:02:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76979875989913a84aa2857423231aca5e92b37d","tid":2074617,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"最新更新：2020/06/22 16:26<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓21日綜合外電報導）前白宮國家安全顧問波頓今天接受美國廣播公司新聞網專訪時直言總統川普不適任，希望他是個「一任總統」，還說川普真以為北韓領導人金正恩愛他，會讓金正恩笑掉大牙。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n在新書出版前，波頓首次受訪，他接受美國廣播公司新聞網（ABC News）主持人拉達茲（Martha Raddatz）訪問，節目今天播出。<br />\n<br />\n波頓表示：「我希望（歷史）將會記得他是個一任總統，不會讓國家沉淪，陷入萬劫不復。一個任期我們還能克服，我有絕對的信心，即使一位保守派的共和黨人11月當選不是什麼奇蹟，當兩任就會讓我更擔心了。」<br />\n<br />\n波頓還說，11月總統大選時，他不會把票投給川普，也不會投給民主黨拜登（Joe Biden），而是會想出一名保守派共和黨人選並寫在選票上。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：李佩珊/核稿：嚴思祺）1090622<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006220188.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202006220188.aspx&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=e286e03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202006220188.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"a5e3fcb4fff53817b1959bcbe3e8be28895af853","tid":2074617,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"保守派共和黨人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少之又少"},{"pid":"2dcefa4d31c9087fd7dfbf81bfe983637fa279ce","tid":2074617,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a5e3fcb4fff53817b1959bcbe3e8be28895af853","tid":2074617,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"保守派共和黨人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少之又少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:16:42.000Z